<font color="#FF0000">WE MUST LISTEN</font><br>
<tt>Fri Dec 13 13:50:28 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
This is an amazing site, one I'll tell anyone who will listen to go find.  It's like being able to read the thoughts behind Maya Lin's extraordinary monument in Washington.  I was born in 1963, and like others above, have hazy memories of a TV war, so I feel it's incumbent on me to find out as much as I can about what it was really like.  Reading the stories, I can't help but feel that there is no healing for some of the suffering that those of you served endure, but I so hope this site will help.  Welcome home, Vietnam Vets!
